<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<!-- @import "head" -->
<body>

  <!-- @import "header" -->

 <main>
  <section class="product-info">
    <div class="product-grid">
      <!-- LEFT -->
      <div>
        <figure class="main-image"><img src="src/assets/img/Armchair-Main.png" alt="Georgian armchair"></figure>

          <div class="thumbnail-grid">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="src/assets/img/Armchair-Main.png" alt="Georgian armchair">
            </div>

            <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="src/assets/img/Yellow-Armchair.png" alt="Georgian armchair side view">
            </div>

            <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="src/assets/img/Yellow-Armchair-Details.png" alt="Georgian armchair detail carving">
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT -->
      <div>
        <h1 class="product-title">Georgian Armchair</h1>
        <p class="product-subtitle">Italian Baroque</p>
        <p class="price">€3,200</p>
        <div class="details-box">
          <div class="detail-item">
            <div class="detail-icon">◷</div>
              <div>
                <p class="detail-label">Auction Date</p>
                <p class="detail-value">15 May 2026</p>
              </div>
          </div>

          <div class="detail-item">
            <div class="detail-icon">⬡</div>
            <div>
              <p class="detail-label">Lot Number</p>
              <p class="detail-value">Lot 17</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="detail-item">
            <div class="detail-icon">i</div>
            <div>
              <p class="detail-label">Category</p>
              <p class="detail-value">Furniture</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <p class="product-description">Majestic armchair with rich upholstery and sculptural wooden details.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="content-section container">
    <div class="content-grid">
    <!-- LEFT CONTENT -->
      <div>
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>Description</h2>
          <p>This commanding Italian Baroque armchair showcases the period's sculptural approach to furniture design. The walnut frame features deeply carved acanthus leaves, scrolling arms terminating in volutes, and cabriole legs with ball-and-claw feet.</p>
          <p>The chair has been reupholstered in period-appropriate Genoese velvet in deep crimson, complementing the rich patina of the carved wood. The overall effect is one of power and prestige.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>History & Provenance</h2>
          <h3>Historical Context</h3>
          <p>Originally created for a Roman palazzo circa 1680–1700, this armchair would have been part of a suite of seat furniture for the main reception room.</p>
          <p>The quality of carving suggests a major workshop, possibly connected to papal commissions. The chair represents the height of Italian Baroque furniture making.</p>
          <h3>Provenance</h3>
          <p>Roman workshop, circa 1690; Italian noble family, Rome, 1690–1850; Acquired by English collector on Grand Tour, 1850; English country house collection, 1850–1975; Professional reupholstery, 2005; Private collection, London, 1975–present.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SPECIFICATIONS -->
        <aside class="specifications">
          <h3>Specifications</h3>
          <div class="spec-group">
            <h4>Dimensions</h4>
            <p>Height: 128 cm</p>
            <p>Width: 72 cm</p>
            <p>Depth: 68 cm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-group">
            <h4>Materials</h4>
            <p>Walnut</p>
            <p>Genoese velvet</p>
            <p>Gilt accents</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="spec-group">
            <h4>Period</h4>
            <p>Italian Baroque</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
  </section>

      <!-- NOTES -->
  <section>
    <div class="notes-grid">
      <div class="note-card">
        <h3>Condition Notes</h3>
        <p>Excellent structural condition. Professionally reupholstered in 2005 using period-appropriate materials and techniques.</p>
        <ul class="notes-list">
          <li>Minor losses to carved details on rear legs</li>
          <li>Historic repair to arm joint (stable and well-executed)</li>
          <li>Some darkening of wood finish on seat rails</li>
          <li>Natural age cracks in wood (stable)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="note-card bid-card">
        <div>
          <h3>Bidding Information</h3>
          <p>Interested in this piece? Register for our upcoming auction to place your bid.</p>
        </div>
          <a href="#" class="btn">View Auction Details</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
  
  <!-- @import "footer" -->
</body>
</html>